Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.75,0:00:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,General.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.20,0:00:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.90,0:00:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.00,0:00:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Exalted minister,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.40,0:00:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you were about to betroth Diāochán to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.70,0:00:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you send her to the Grand Preceptor?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.60,0:00:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,General! Please, calm down! Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.90,0:00:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,General, you misunderstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.52,0:00:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.74,0:01:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.28,0:01:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that you sent Diāochán in a carriage\Nto the Premier's mansion as a gift!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.34,0:01:14.06,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(131,352)\fade(255,0,255,0,510,2345,2700)}Wáng Yǔn\NStyled: Zishī
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.04,0:01:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably don't know this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.66,0:01:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, in court,\N the Grand Preceptor told me,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.04,0:01:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'll come to your household tomorrow, \N I have something to discuss."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.20,0:01:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So I prepared a small feast for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.74,0:01:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,While he was drinking, he said,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.12,0:01:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,"I heard you have a daughter named Diāochán"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"that you betrothed to my son, Fèngxiān."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.22,0:01:42.86,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(101,332)\fade(255,0,255,0,490,2150,2620)}Lǚ Bù\NStyled: Fèngxiān
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.68,0:01:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"I was afraid it was undecided,"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"so I'm here to confirm and meet her as well."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.70,0:01:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I dare not let him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So I led Diāochán to greet the Grand Preceptor,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.14,0:01:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and he said, "Today is a good day!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,"Allow me to take this girl to marry Fèngxiān."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.25,0:02:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Imagine, General,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.00,0:02:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,the Grand Preceptor came to pick her up in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I dare refuse him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.54,0:02:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So I had to send my daughter over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.18,0:02:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.40,0:02:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to have troubled you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.34,0:02:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe you my humblest apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.44,0:02:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,General, you didn't know, \Nwhat's there to apologize for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the Grand Preceptor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.40,0:03:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The Grand Preceptor is sleeping with his new bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.18,0:03:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't got up yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.36,0:03:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Which new bride?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl named Diāochán.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.98,0:03:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Diāochán?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.34,0:03:32.54,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(243,324)\fade(255,0,255,0,490,1980,2180)}Diāochán
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here, darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.95,0:04:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Fèngxiān, my son! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.02,0:04:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No... nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.62,0:04:37.00,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(128,353)\fade(255,0,255,0,495,2555,5555)}Dǒng Zhuō\NStyled: Zhòngyǐng
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare to desire my mistress?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here! You are forbidden to enter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.52,0:06:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's present?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The Grand Preceptor sent this servant to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He said the Marquis of Wēn from\N now on can enter his mansion
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,as if it was your own home, \Nno need to be formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That senile lech!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.52,0:06:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He dares to mock me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,General, why aren't you in court \Nwith the Grand Preceptor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not safe to talk here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You may first go to\NFèngyí Pavillion and wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.40,0:09:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,General, though I am not\NMinister Wáng's natural daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,he treats me like I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.05,0:09:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I fell for you at first sight, my general.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So he betrothed me to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I hoped I could depend on you all my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:10:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but the lecherous Grand Preceptor deflowered me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't kill myself there only\Nbecause I wanted to say farewell to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to endure humiliation just to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.98,0:10:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Luckily today, I was able \Nto see you General.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.98,0:10:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,My wish has been fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My body has been defiled. \NI cannot be with you any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.80,0:10:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I only wish you see me one last time, general!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've long known your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:10:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I only regret not being together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be your wife in this life. \NWe'll have to meet in the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If I cannot marry you in this life,\Nthen I am no hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, a day here is like a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I force a smile before him and weep behind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take pity, General! Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.14,0:12:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Has Fèngxiān been here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He went to the inner hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I've come unannounced,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,fearing the old lech will see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.16,0:12:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.94,0:12:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to leave now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.46,0:12:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.44,0:12:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,General, if you are so afraid of that old lech,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.82,0:12:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,then I will never get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me time, I'll think of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Diāochán at?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.86,0:12:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in the garden admiring the flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:13:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was in my boudoir, \NI heard of your great name
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,like thunder piercing the ears.\NI thought you were the greatest hero of this era,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,but instead, even you \Nare controlled by others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand Preceptor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.22,0:14:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I've.. I've came to your mansion\N when I learnt that you were furious
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.12,0:14:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and went straight to the\N back garden to look for Lǚ Bù.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.20,0:14:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I came and saw Lǚ Bù escaping. He was shouting,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.62,0:14:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Grand Preceptor wants to kill me!".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.22,0:14:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I've rushed here to mediate peace\N but accidentally bumped into you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard whelp! He has the guts to have an affair with my mistress?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down! Grand Preceptor, \Ncalm down! That won't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.50,0:14:46.70,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(592,278)\fade(255,0,255,0,590,2820,3180)}Lǐ Rú
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.86,0:14:53.86,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: King Zhuāng of Chǔ was one of the Five Hegemons of the Spring and Autumn period.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.88,0:14:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Sir, of old, King Zhuāng of Chǔ hosted a feast with his retainers one night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.74,0:15:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}When the candle was out, Jiǎng Xióng took advantage to flirt with the queen,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.34,0:15:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}but the queen ripped the tassel from his hat
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}and asked King Zhuāng of Chǔ to light the candle to reveal the offender,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}but King Zhuāng of Chǔ ordered all the retainers to remove their tassels
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}so the lights wouldn't indicate the offender.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}After King Zhuāng of Chǔ was surrounded by Qín troops,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Jiǎng Xióng risked his life to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.30,0:15:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}At present, Diāochán is merely just a woman
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.94,0:15:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}and Lǚ Bù is your most trusted and fierce general.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.32,0:15:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Grand Preceptor, if you can seize this opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.78,0:15:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}and give Diāochán to Lǚ Bù,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.55,0:15:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Lǚ Bù will remember this kindness and will definitely repay you with his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Consider the advantages.\NI hope that sir understands this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Slut!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.62,0:16:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare have an affair with Lǚ Bù?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.76,0:16:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand Preceptor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand Preceptor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.62,0:16:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand Preceptor, I was only admiring \Nthe flowers in the garden,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.46,0:16:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,when Lǚ Bù suddenly came. \NI wanted to avoid him,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but he said, "I am the Grand Preceptor's son. \NWhy must you avoid me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.36,0:16:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,With these words, he forced me to Fèngyí Pavilion with his halberd.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.14,0:16:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew he had no good intentions
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was afraid he'd assail me and disgrace you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,so I intended to drown myself in the lotus pond.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But he held me from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I was between life and death \Nwhen you came and saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.94,0:17:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your forgiveness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I were to send you to Lǚ Bù?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.48,0:18:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How does it sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I would rather die than be disgraced!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I was only joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.38,0:18:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be Lǐ Rú's idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a profound friendship with Lǚ Bù
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,so he set up this plan regardless of your honor, and my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.00,0:19:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I have the heart to give you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Although you love me dearly,\N I'm afraid we cannot stay here for long,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.88,0:19:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,or Lǚ Bù will certainly hurt us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, we'll live together in Méiwù!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.66,0:19:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You can enjoy a joyful life there,\N carefree and without worries!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Many thanks, Grand Preceptor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand Preceptor, today is a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.18,0:19:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You can send Diāochán to Fèngxiān now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:20:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But Lǚ Bù and I are father and son!\NIt's improper!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ignore his crimes, nevermind them. \NYou can go reassure him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Grand Preceptor, you can't be fooled by that woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you willing to give your concubine to Lǚ Bù or not? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.44,0:20:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not talk about Diāochán ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.46,0:20:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who speaks of this again will be executed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.00,0:21:13.36,Thinking,,0,0,0,,All of us will die in the hands of that woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.00,0:21:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,General! General!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.26,0:21:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The other day I caught a cold, so I couldn't come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I haven't seen you for a long time, General.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, the Grand Preceptor rode to Méiwù,\N I had to see him off despite my illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.48,0:21:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you follow him there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.90,0:22:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,May I ask why you are sighing, General?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.90,0:22:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of your daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.25,0:22:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,After all this time, the Grand Preceptor \Nstill hasn't sent my daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.00,0:22:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That lech has kept her for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.32,0:22:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.34,0:22:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do I even start!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.26,0:22:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we discuss this in my humble abode. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.54,0:23:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I never imagined that the Grand Preceptor\Ncould do something this barbaric!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.12,0:23:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He has not only defiled my daughter, \Nbut took your wife as a concubine, General!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.35,0:23:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be the ridicule of the whole nation!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.42,0:23:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They are not laughing at \Nthe Grand Preceptor, but at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.00,0:23:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It matters not whether I am \Nridiculed as senile or incompetent,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.72,0:23:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're the peerless hero of the realm!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.32,0:24:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you bear such a humiliation and shame?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.00,0:24:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologies for letting these\N words slip, please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.96,0:24:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I will kill that senile wretch! Avenge my disgrace!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.55,0:24:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,General, General!\NDon't get into trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.82,0:24:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A real man should stand up\N between Heaven and Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.00,0:24:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I submit to him any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.00,0:24:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are a great general,\Nhow could the Grand Preceptor restrain you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.11,0:24:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I will butcher that bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.44,0:24:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.22,0:24:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet I have a father and son bond,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.14,0:24:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I fear what later generations will say about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.78,0:25:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,General, your surname is Lǚ, \Nbut his surname is Dǒng.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.22,0:25:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Consider this:
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.86,0:25:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,At Fèngyí Pavillion, when he threw your halberd at you...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.46,0:25:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,where was the bond then?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.20,0:25:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, if not for your words, I would be amiss
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.14,0:25:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,General, if you can revive the Imperial House of Hàn,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.20,0:25:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll be known as a loyal officer,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.02,0:25:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and your name will be \Nimmortalized in history!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.90,0:25:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,General, if you aid Dǒng Zhuó...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.06,0:25:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll be known as a traitor, \Nand go down in history as a byword of infamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.00,0:25:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Pros and cons, advantages and disadvantages.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.56,0:26:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,To be pure or impure, to be loyal or disloyal.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.20,0:26:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,General, please consider this!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.20,0:26:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, your words have cleared my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.26,0:26:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I am determined! \NDo not doubt me sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.00,0:26:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.14,0:26:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.96,0:26:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,it's just that if our plan fails, we will be in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.64,0:26:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}I swear to revive the Hàn state by killing the national traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.72,0:26:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}If I ever betray my word,\Nthen doom me for all of eternity!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.55,0:27:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.04,0:27:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}If the House of Hàn doesn't fall, it's thanks to you, General.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.70,0:27:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Please accept my respects!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.22,0:27:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.52,0:27:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Does the Minister have any plans to eliminate the traitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.74,0:27:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}I'll tell you it when the time has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.44,0:27:52.96,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Dǒng Zhuō is far away in Méiwù.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.44,0:28:00.92,Thinking,,0,0,0,,We could send an eloquent man to Méiwù asking him to come to court to discuss matters,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.90,0:28:07.30,Thinking,,0,0,0,,but who to send?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.33,0:28:12.04,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Lǐ Sù was originally one of Dǒng Zhuó's supporters.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.10,0:28:18.22,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He once enticed Lǚ Bù to kill Dīng Yuán \Nbut Dǒng Zhuó did not promote him afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.72,0:28:20.36,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He harbors a grudge due to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.48,0:28:25.76,Thinking,,0,0,0,,If we send Lǐ Sù,\Nthat traitor won't be suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.94,0:28:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, sires.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.97,0:28:35.24,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(108,315)}Lǐ Sù
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.96,0:28:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Exalted sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.66,0:28:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Please sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.72,0:28:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.42,0:28:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.73,0:29:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Sù, back then, you induced me to kill Dīng Jiànyáng and turn to Dǒng Zhuó.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.30,0:29:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Now this lech abuses the Emperor\Nand oppresses the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.44,0:29:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,His sins are innumerable and the people and gods have a common resentment!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.56,0:29:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the Exalted Minister asks you, Brother Sù,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.62,0:29:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to spread an imperial edict throughout Méiwù biding Dǒng Zhuō to enter the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.78,0:29:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I will pretend to be subservient while the warriors wait within the gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.81,0:29:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,By killing this traitor, we would help the Hàn Empire and we'll be known as loyal ministers.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.99,0:29:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your honorable opinion?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.72,0:29:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Exalted Minister!\N Thank you, General!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.63,0:29:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I have long wanted to kill that traitor Dǒng!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.98,0:29:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I only regret I wasn't able to find any allies.\NNow we have been
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.70,0:29:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,bestowed an opportunity by heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.92,0:29:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My mind is set!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.98,0:30:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,General, please go straight to Méiwù.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.85,0:30:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}My dear concubine, I dreamt \Nof a dragon covering my body last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.62,0:30:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Sure enough, good news came today when
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.38,0:30:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}the Son of Heaven sent for me to enter the court
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.08,0:30:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}and abdicate the throne to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.50,0:30:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Minister Wáng already built an abdication platform for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.36,0:30:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}They're just waiting for me to accept the throne!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.12,0:30:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}After I become the Son of Heaven,\N you will be my favored concubine!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.58,0:31:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your great favor, my lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.20,0:31:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful girl, you just wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.92,0:31:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come to take you to the palace soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.25,0:31:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}The carriage's wheel broke\Nand the horse escaped its reins,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.78,0:31:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}what omens do they bode?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.08,0:31:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}My lord, it bodes you will ascend the throne,\Nabandon the old for the new.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.56,0:31:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}These omens mean you will ride in the Emperor's jade carriage on a golden saddle!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.81,0:31:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Heavens really blessed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.35,0:32:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}The grass spreads a thousand lǐ, how green it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.65,0:32:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Within 10 days, it won't be alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.16,0:32:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The grass spreads a thousand lǐ, how green it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.52,0:32:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that song bode well or ill fortunes?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.20,0:32:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It bodes the Liú clan will be gone and Dǒng clan will thrive!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.46,0:32:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop singing! Stop singing!\NGo play over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.20,0:32:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with singing?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.35,0:32:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what the song means?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.45,0:32:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}'Thousand' 'lǐ' 'grass' refers to the character 'Dǒng',
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.42,0:32:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}'Ten' 'days' refers to the character 'Zhuó',
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.20,0:32:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}It means that Dǒng Zhuó won't live!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.10,0:32:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}You want to die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.46,0:33:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Heaven blesses us.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.58,0:33:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Heaven blesses us.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.95,0:33:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Heaven blesses us.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.56,0:34:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My respects, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.00,0:34:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright! It's alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.80,0:34:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.72,0:34:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,After I accept the Emperor's abdication,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.70,0:34:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you will be in charge of all the military forces throughout the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.88,0:34:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, father!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.86,0:34:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't Wáng Yǔn and Lǐ Rú here?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.56,0:34:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wáng Yǔn is on the abdication platform waiting\N for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.78,0:35:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Lǐ Rú caught an illness, so he could not come.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.86,0:35:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your son respectfully invites you, father, \Nto ascend the platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.30,0:35:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.38,0:35:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.66,0:36:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The traitor scum has arrived! \NSummon the warriors!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.57,0:36:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is my son Fèngxiān?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.41,0:36:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is the imperial order! Kill the treacherous \Nminister Dǒng Zhuó! The rest will be pardoned!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.11,0:36:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Fèngxiān, my son! Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.77,0:36:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard! We cannot coexist together!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.82,0:36:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him!
